query: SELECT ml.*, r.name as region_name FROM monitoring_logs ml LEFT JOIN regions r ON ml.region_id = r.id WHERE ml.created_at > '2026-01-02 10:44:00' ORDER BY ml.created_at DESC LIMIT 5
